description: A very cool looking guy came to my office today. He was nicely dressed and very polite. Still he gave me sort of a rebellious vibe. He worked as a bartender at a small town in the eastern part of the country and wanted to start a new life in Prague. I found him a pretty sweet job as a car salesman, which he really liked. He was only one step from his dream life in the capital. Now was the time to find out if this stylish boy had a naughty side. He had a big tattoo on his chest, which was a good sign… But I had to dig deep into my pocket to convince him to go further. He wanted to stay faithful to his beloved girlfriend, how romantic… Unfortunately for his virgin ass, I had a lot of money. If you enjoy watching straight boys struggling during their first ass fuck, you will love this.
title: Dirty Scout 156
